{"type": "article", "id": 14778, "title": "Armis Helmet 头盔", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-11T07:11:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000327ZGRT5Ml1WfvCBDJy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自美国的设计师 Robin Spicer 设计了一组 Armis Helmet 头盔，其中的黑白款外形酷似企鹅。皮质的开口虽然利于通风，但似乎不利于安全，因而设计师配上了目前头盔市场上最流行的安全系统MIPS（Multi-directional Impact Protection System），即多向冲击保护系统，用内层塑料罩减少摔车等紧急情况对脑部带来的首次冲击。是同时内置了一个碰撞传感器，在遇到紧急情况时可以发出警报。<a href=\"http://www.robinspicerdesign.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142225amg2YlTAFG8febO6.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142226Wp5dDaO9wyE1U0ZT.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142227z3Xi7hYHjERG9Z6x.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142227tq2H8QvdxcaBgNFp.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"591\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}